CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Key Tronic Corp is an electronic manufacturing service provider. The company provides electronic manufacturing services to original equipment manufacturers in the United States and globally. Its primary services include product assembly, plastic molding, precision metal stamping, fabrication and finishing and engineering services and in-house testing. The firm derives a majority of its revenue from the United States.
